Title: Bernoulli-like polynomials associated with Stirling Numbers
Authors: Carl M. Bender, Dorje C. Brody, and Bernhard K. Meister
Categories: math-ph math.MP
Comments: 3 pages
\\
  The Stirling numbers of the first kind can be represented in terms of a new
class of polynomials that are closely related to the Bernoulli polynomials.
Recursion relations for these polynomials are given.
